commit.message:
builtins.c (java_builtins): Add acos, asin, ceil and floor.


	* builtins.c (java_builtins): Add acos, asin, ceil and floor.
	(initialize_builtins): Likewise, define acos, asin, ceil and floor.

	* testsuite/libjava.lang/MathBuiltin.java: Add tests for acos, asin,
	ceil and floor.

From-SVN: r81341
